---
subject: "[{{ convention.name }}] {{ ticket.ticket_type.description | titleize }} Purchase Receipt"
---
Thanks for purchasing a {{ convention.ticket_name }} for {{ convention.name }}!  Your receipt is below.

<hr/>

<dl class="dl-horizontal">
  <dt class="col-md-3">Purchaser</dt>
  <dd class="col-md-9">
    {{ ticket.user_con_profile.name_without_nickname }}
  </dd>
  <dt class="col-md-3">Type</dt>
  <dd class="col-md-9">
    {{ ticket.ticket_type.description }}
  </dd>
  {% if ticket.provided_by_event %}
    <dt class="col-md-3">Provided by event</dt>
    <dd class="col-md-9">
      {{ ticket.provided_by_event.title }}
    </dd>
  {% endif %}
  <dt class="col-md-3">Paid</dt>
  <dd class="col-md-9">
    {% if ticket.payment_amount && ticket.payment_amount.fractional > 0 %}
      {{ ticket.payment_amount.format }}
    {% else %}
      0
    {% endif %}
  </dd>
  <dt class="col-md-3">Transaction ID</dt>
  <dd class="col-md-9">
    {% if ticket.payment_amount && ticket.payment_amount.fractional > 0 %}
      {{ ticket.charge_id }}
    {% endif %}
  </dd>
  <dt class="col-md-3">Created</dt>
  <dd class="col-md-9">
    {{ ticket.created_at | date:"%B %e, %Y %l:%M %p %Z" }}
  </dd>
  <dt class="col-md-3">Last updated</dt>
  <dd class="col-md-9">
    {{ ticket.updated_at | date:"%B %e, %Y %l:%M %p %Z" }}
  </dd>
</dl>
